Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:09.18,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Fenrir, an S-Rank monster capable \Nof destroying a major city by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.98,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,A village under constant \Nattack from this beast
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:14.53,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,has spent nearly all of their savings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.76,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,to hire us, the Flaming \NDragon Fang, to defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.05,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Bandana!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:35.22,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:47.88,Default,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:56.28,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Do it, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.40,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Bandana, the swift Ranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.28,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Marlefiss, the Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.40,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,And Golnova, the flaming Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.37,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,After defeating Fenrir,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.59,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,we, the Flaming Dragon Fang, \Nbecame a party of heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.62,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,My story is one you don't hear so often—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:37.13,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,that of a powerless man \Nin a party full of heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:44.14,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,who handles their chores on \Na journey to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.13,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,This tastes like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.24,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Is this village incapable \Nof serving decent food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:55.85,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Hey, Kur!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.85,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Make me something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.33,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.92,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'll prepare something right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:05.48,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Today's the last day we get \Nto eat Kur's cooking, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.22,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.88,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Um, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.96,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Not the sharpest, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.40,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,It means you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.27,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.36,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:18.71,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,More like, you haven't done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.32,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,You just do chores \Nand can't even defeat a slime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.67,Default,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,Parties can only have four members.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.79,Default,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,That is the law of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:33.13,Default,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,If we want to become even stronger, \Nwe'll need to recruit a high-ranked mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.35,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,That means we need to drop \Nsomeone from the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.46,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,You might carry our bags for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.22,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,but you're basically baggage yourself, Kur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:43.18,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.06,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Please, Golnova!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.93,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Please let me stay in the party—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.10,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:00.39,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Turns out, my story is one \Nyou hear all too often—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:06.42,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,that of powerless man kicked out \Nof a party full of heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:10.16,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,who now travels with nowhere to go.
