Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.60,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,So this is Hello Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.61,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm so anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.36,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,But I need to earn money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.84,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.55,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Samaela Branch \Nof Hello, Hello Work Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.42,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Are you looking for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.32,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Or are you looking to hire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:12.16,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,U-Um... I'm looking for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.31,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.82,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,we'll start with an interview \Nand an aptitude test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.68,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Could you start by telling me \Nyour name and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.15,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.52,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,My name is Kurt Rockhans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.09,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm 15 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.98,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Kurt, you said? Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:33.65,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Hast Village, in the Sheen Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.81,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was a village out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.70,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,What kind of work have you done so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.00,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:45.78,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I handled various chores for the \Nadventuring party Flaming Dragon Fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.78,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,The one that was promoted \Nto SS-Rank the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.66,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,They fired me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:56.62,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Even so, I'm sure it'll be quite \Nthe feather in your cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:00.44,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,People will look upon me favorably \Njust for handling chores there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.70,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Golnova and the others really are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:07.05,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Now, let's move on to your aptitude test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:11.31,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,As you know, your aptitudes are \Nthe talents granted to you by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:15.93,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Perhaps we'll be able to uncover \Nsome hidden talents of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.28,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:23.57,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Aptitudes are rated from G-Rank, \Nmeaning no talent at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.97,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,all the way up to SSS-Rank, the highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:31.32,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,While someone with a low aptitude for \Nswordsmanship may not be able to cut steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:34.19,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,someone with a high aptitude could \Nsplit it in two with the same sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.36,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Maybe I have my own hidden talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:44.04,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,They're all... G-Rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:50.18,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,The results show that you have \Nno talent for any combat skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.69,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but this will limit \Nthe work you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.81,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,There's still trade work, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:01.17,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,We haven't tested your aptitude for things \Nlike blacksmithing or alchemy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.13,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Though our technician is currently absent,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.37,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,so you'll have to wait about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.70,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Um, to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.81,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I barely have any money left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.33,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:14.70,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.49,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,could you try lifting that sandbag there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.12,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.61,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:25.89,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,It felt like it drained a bit of my mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.51,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,It's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.53,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Okay, that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.69,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,If you're that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.36,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,then you should be able to \Nhandle construction work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:44.17,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,A frontier town in the \NMargraviate of Taicone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.57,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,is recruiting workers to \Nrepair their city walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.30,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Would you like to work there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:49.86,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.52,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Then I'll prepare a letter \Nof introduction for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:55.08,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I found work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.00,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,A temp worker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.95,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:07.20,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Well, we {\i1}are{\i0} shorthanded, \Nso we can't be picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:11.49,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Listen, boy. I'm only going to \Nsay this once, so pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.47,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.99,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Make cement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:14.68,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.50,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Then mend the walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.26,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.20,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.58,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Do I not need to go through \Nthe process of pouring mana
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.10,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,into the cement to strengthen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.13,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.46,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,I'll come check on you in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:28.65,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Make sure you've gone through \Nat least half a barrel's worth by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.84,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Your pay's based on performance, \Nso you'll lose money if you slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.50,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I guess pouring mana into it \Nis such common knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.85,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,that he doesn't even need \Nto explain that part?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.94,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I must seem pretty unreliable to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.63,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm surprised half a barrel is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:46.22,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,But I'll give it my all \Ninstead of taking it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:56.47,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.97,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.58,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I ran out of cement, \Nso this was as far as I could get!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.69,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,You... ran out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:07.17,DefaultItalics,Alraid,0,0,0,,He repaired a whole third \Nof the huge western wall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.88,DefaultItalics,Alraid,0,0,0,,in just three hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.31,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,How did you even handle the upper parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.28,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,I don't see any scaffolds or ladders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:18.27,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I scooped up the cement, threw it into place,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.69,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,and then rolled it out with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.85,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,There's no way you could—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.26,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,No, it's clear that you already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.08,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,How much longer can you work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:35.51,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I was hoping to work here for about a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:36.93,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.57,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,All right. That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:45.00,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Sorry, but this is all \NI can pay you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.13,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,I'll transfer the rest of your pay \Nlater through Hello Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.84,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Are you sure about paying me this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.41,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.44,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Now take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.62,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,He paid me so much after saying \Nit was based on performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.64,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,All right, I'll do my best tomorrow, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.80,Default,Laborer,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.80,DefaultTop,Laborer,0,0,0,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:02.58,Default,Laborer,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.09,Default,Laborer,0,0,0,,I heard they finished repairs \Non the west and north walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:05.92,Default,Laborer,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.67,DefaultTop,Laborer,0,0,0,,Is there any work left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:09.50,Default,Laborer,0,0,0,,Three days ago, there was only a portion \Nof the western wall done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.69,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,You don't need to come back after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:12.92,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.67,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,But it's only been three days—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:19.13,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,The wall repairs were supposed to \Nprovide work to those in poverty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.72,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,If you stay here any longer, \Nthere won't be anything left for the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.37,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.85,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,You work too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.37,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Too fast? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.91,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,At any rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:33.52,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,The ability you demonstrated here \Nis on par with SS-Rank, if not SSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:36.49,DefaultTop,Alraid,0,0,0,,Get out of here and go \Nwork in the royal capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.89,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,S?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.26,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Here's the rest of your pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.25,Default,Alraid,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:45.41,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Did he want to get rid of me so badly \Nthat he flattered me and paid me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.04,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,It didn't work out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.58,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.07,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.93,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,But what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:57.04,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,There's still a few more days \Nbefore our technician arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.55,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Why can't you accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:02.73,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,No one will take on a job \Nwith those conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:05.01,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You won't know until you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:07.32,DefaultTop,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Please keep my conditions as-is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.32,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,She's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.89,DefaultTop,Staff,0,0,0,,We can't accept it, \Nno matter how hard you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.48,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Kurt, please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.57,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.84,DefaultTop,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}your{\i0} job to find someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.14,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,What seems to be the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.17,DefaultTop,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I don't have time to—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:16.40,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,This woman is looking to hire a miner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.50,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,However, she insists on paying \Nbased on successful results
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.59,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,without any advance payment \Nfor an unproven mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.88,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Madam, if those are your conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:30.50,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,then I recommend you recruit investors \Nto develop a mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.22,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,If I don't pay the taxes within a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.29,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,then they'll impound the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.24,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,That's a tough position to be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.67,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:42.49,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Would I be able to take on the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.22,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.67,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Back in my village,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:47.43,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I used to help excavate in the mines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.88,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:51.92,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,To be honest, you can't expect \Nto be paid for it, Kurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.51,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:58.85,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I want to hire someone like a brawny dwarf, \Nnot a helpless child like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:03.12,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,In that case, you'll need \Nto prepare 10 silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.88,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,If I had that kind of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.18,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:13.54,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Uh, Kurt, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.63,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You do have experience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:16.95,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.25,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.49,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:23.71,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.55,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.87,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Honestly, Kurt is too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.56,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,With his adorable looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.95,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,he'd be better off working \Nin the pleasure quarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.77,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Ah! Kirshell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.19,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Kirshell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.19,DefaultTop,Staff,0,0,0,,Kirshell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.32,DefaultTop,Kurt,0,0,0,,Kirshell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:45.00,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Kirshell, we've received a bank transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.07,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Kirshell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.75,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.01,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I-I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.96,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,This is the construction work pay \Nto be deposited in Kurt's account, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:58.80,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:03.23,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Two hundred gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.21,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Wha? Huh? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:08.94,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Kirshell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.24,DefaultTop,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.24,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.56,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.34,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,What are these sandbags doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.89,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,We're returning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.07,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,By the way, those aren't sandbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:21.12,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,They're used to measure how much mana \Na person possesses in their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.63,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,They get heavier the more mana a person has,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.70,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,but they generally don't react \Nto normal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.92,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,It takes mana on the level of a royal \Ncourt mage to activate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.49,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,so they're hard to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.43,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.06,Default,Senior,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, could you \Nmove them outside for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.12,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.46,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,It's heavy, but not {\i1}that{\i0} heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:48.35,DefaultItalics,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Kurt, who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.51,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.30,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, there's only one tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:08.32,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's big enough for two people to sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:11.03,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,We're both sleeping in the same tent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.97,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Are you an incredibly restless \Nsleeper or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.51,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:19.48,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I can't share a tent with a \Ncute woman like you, Yulishia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.46,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.42,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Cute? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.61,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.16,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.47,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I've traveled the whole world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.30,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,and I've never seen anyone else \Nas beautiful as you, Yulishia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.64,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't say another word!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.39,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I've been adventuring since I was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.10,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.59,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Now, stop saying weird things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.59,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Come on! Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.16,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,You cooked this, Yulishia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:57.17,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,This hardly counts as cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.62,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I just boiled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:04.72,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,It's been a long time \Nsince anyone cooked for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:05.96,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,so I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:16.16,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Golnova and the others \Nnever even ate with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.26,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.21,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.24,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I-I can't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.69,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I wonder if Yulishia's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:53.85,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yulishia, you're too trusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:56.25,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm a man too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.72,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,We'll be together for a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:06.69,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,so I was planning to use this night to determine\Nif he's the kind of guy who'd assault me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.24,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,He's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.64,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,More importantly, he's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.41,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I mean, he'll be fun to tease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.25,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Did he sleep outside all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.46,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh? It's fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.42,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,With a new button, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.61,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Yulishia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:41.69,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Did you fix my clothes for me, Kurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.85,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.24,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.67,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.56,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:51.99,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,This boy is definitely \Nworking in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.66,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Let's head out once you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.00,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,We need to earn ten gold \Nbefore the week is up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.46,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:03.14,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Um, so have you decided \Nwhere to start digging?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.88,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,No, we'll just start digging \Nfrom somewhere nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:06.75,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:10.92,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Uh, you won't find any ore \Nif you just dig at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.92,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.27,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.89,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,In that case, I'd like to take \Na quick look around for something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.22,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,so please follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.21,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:24.60,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,This is what we want. \NWhen you split one of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.38,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:28.06,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that's a gemstone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.01,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,It's a crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.03,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,One this big should go for around three gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:36.15,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,We've already hit a third of our goal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.29,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:42.37,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I've finished looking into \Nthe rocks around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.58,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.31,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Uh, so the next step is to sell these, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.21,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.95,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:53.13,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Yeah, you did find all of them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:56.96,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,All but the first one are too small \Nto be worth very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.72,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,so we'll turn them into magic crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.68,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.73,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I thought there were fewer \Nthan ten magic craftsmen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.70,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,in the kingdom capable of \Nmanufacturing magic crystals...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.02,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.39,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You're done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:12.01,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I heard that it takes at least \Nan hour to make even the smallest one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.34,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,A whole hour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.57,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I don't have much mana, \Nso I couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:21.83,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,So real magic craftsmen are capable \Nof emitting mana for a whole hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.82,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I get the feeling we're not on the same page.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.46,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Are you really staying here, Kurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.04,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes. There are things I'd like to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.05,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:37.29,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I should be back tomorrow morning \Nafter I sell the magic crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:38.89,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.94,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Take care, Yulishia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.35,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Ah, damn it, he's just too damn cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.21,Default,Inspector,0,0,0,,You have magic crystals?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:52.44,Default,Inspector,0,0,0,,Do you have the proper documents \Nfor crystals from abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.20,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,These were produced domestically, so I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:56.90,Default,Inspector,0,0,0,,Domestically?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.36,Default,Inspector,0,0,0,,By which atelier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.50,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Of course they'd ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:06.69,Default,Inspector,0,0,0,,You're an adventurer serving \Ndirectly under the royal family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.92,Default,Inspector,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:10.23,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Could I use your teleportation stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.67,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I need to go to the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:15.55,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I only {\i0}used{\i1} to serve under \Nthe royal family, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:20.77,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Well, even if I told them the truth about\Nthese crystals, it's not like they'd believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:23.64,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.60,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Yulishia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.02,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I'm actually here on business today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.65,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I was thinking of having you \Nbuy these from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.72,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Magic crystals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.03,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Their glow doesn't seem that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.15,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,so they're probably not worth much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.15,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,About 10 silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.83,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Around that much, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.19,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Huh? This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.90,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:52.24,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Given how he made them, \NI'm not surprised they don't go for much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.17,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Yulishia, I can buy this \Nfrom you for 10 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.42,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:03.05,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,This magic crystal has ten times the \Nusual amount of mana imbued in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.44,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Even though its glow is so dim?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.09,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,It's not glowing very much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:10.98,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,because it's been treated to prevent \Nthe mana inside from leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.38,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I have 49 more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.19,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Here, 500 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.15,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,But can I ask two things of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.36,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:26.27,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,don't sell these magic crystals \Nanywhere but my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:30.76,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,I doubt any other shops would \Nunderstand their proper value,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:35.82,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,and our kingdom wouldn't want magic crystals \Nthis strong out in regular circulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.59,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,What's the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.05,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Tell me who made these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.49,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,That I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.51,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.50,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Someone who can make \Nmagic crystals this strong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.69,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,should be working directly for the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.95,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Or are you trying to monopolize them \Nfor your own profit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.53,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,That isn't why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:57.87,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I just don't want to share information \Nabout them without their permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.18,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Yulishia, this is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:04.25,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,By the power vested in me as a royal court mage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.72,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,with status equal to an Honorary Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.71,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I don't serve directly under \Nthe royal family anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.85,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I'm not obligated to obey your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:16.13,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,And yet you seem to have no issue taking \Nadvantage of your old status when it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.35,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.67,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Then let me ask as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:27.19,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Please do everything you can to prevent \Nthem from wandering off to another nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.83,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Also, please inform them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:33.51,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,that we can offer them the directorship \Nof a royal magic technology research lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:35.32,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,with the title of Honorary Baron,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:39.04,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,possibly Honorary Count pending the \Nproper permission from His Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:41.42,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:52.09,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,She paid me 500 gold and wants to make \NKurt a director and a Honorary Count?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:53.72,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,This doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.50,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. We've already closed for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.00,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Oh, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.46,DefaultTop,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I want to ask you a few things about Kurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.46,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I want to ask you a few things about Kurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.36,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:08.00,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Just who in the world {\i1}is{\i0} Kurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:12.67,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. We have a duty to protect \Nthe confidentiality of our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:21.64,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh? Kurt was a part of \Nthe Flaming Dragon Fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.83,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:25.32,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,And yet he's G-Rank across the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:28.82,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,He was fired from his job repairing \Ncastle walls after three days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:30.40,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,but his payment was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:32.03,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Two hundred gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:36.75,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,They said he finished repairing both the \Nnorthern and western walls by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.77,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,No wonder they had to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:43.42,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:47.50,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Also, please deposit this \Ninto Kurt's account, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:48.69,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:50.47,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's 499 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:51.47,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:56.56,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Also, I'm ordering you as an adventurer \Ndirectly serving under the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:01.88,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You are hereby forbidden to divulge \Nany information about Kurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:03.50,Default,Kirshell,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:14.95,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, Yulishia, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:18.31,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Uh... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:22.57,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I built it while you were away in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.31,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Incidentally, Kurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:28.92,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,what are your thoughts on constructing \Nan entire house in a single night?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:29.75,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:32.65,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,People did it all the time in my hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:34.35,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,so it's nothing special, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:37.46,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,There's no way that's normal!
